text: It really feels like I'm wearing a party dress.

Well, considering the venue,
it fits perfectly!

Hehe...
Yes, I think so too.
It's fitting for the occasion, isn't it?

I was surprised when I saw the design...
I never expected to get a job that would suit it so well.

Haha,
it's not every day you get a job at a party venue.

I heard we're free to do as we please when we're not on
stage. They said we should eat and drink plenty.

The outfit is one thing,
but I also need to be mindful of my behavior...

Producer, if I do anything rude,
please be sure to point it out to me...!
